				</div>
                				<h4><a href="//www.nytimes.com/2015/02/18/business/international/greece-bureaucracy-not-just-austerity-is-an-economic-drag.html?ref=dealbook">Greek Bureaucracy, Not Just Austerity, Is an Economic Drag</a></h4>
				<p class="nyt-article-byline">By LIZ ALDERMAN</p>
				<p class="nyt-article-summary">Many business owners say relief from austerity measures imposed by foreign creditors will not be enough to reinvigorate growth.</p>
			</div>
			
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><em>Hugo Dixon is co-founder of Breakingviews and editor-at-large at Reuters News. For more independent commentary and analysis, visit<a href="//www.breakingviews.com/home/"> breakingviews.com</a>.<br />
</em></p>
